OL,3,CTravel disruption and high winds as
OL,4,CStorm Dave batters North West
OL,6,FRetreat Adlington, a restaurant near
OL,7,FChorley recorded the moment the storm
OL,8,Fbrought down a tree onto the train
OL,9,Fline running to Preston and Blackpool
OL,11,FHigh winds and heavy rain has caused
OL,12,Ftravel disruption across the North
OL,13,FWest as Storm Dave brought down trees
OL,14,Fand blocked railway lines.
OL,16,FYellow warnings of wind across parts
OL,17,Fof northern England were lifted early
OL,18,Fon Easter Sunday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
