PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775426988
OL,3,CTravel disruption and high winds as
OL,4,CStorm Dave batters North West
OL,6,FIn Heaton Moor, Stockport, a large
OL,7,Ftree came down damaging the roof and
OL,8,Fwindows of a block of flats. The
OL,9,Fproperty was cordoned off by Greater
OL,10,FManchester Fire Rescue Service after
OL,11,Fthe fallen tree uprooted the pavement
OL,12,Fon Heaton Moor Road.
